      "span_text": "The included retrospective trials were evaluated by 2 authors (BCW and LLS) and their results assessed using 9 star Newcastle-Ottawa scale.  The Newcastle-Ottawa scale assesses trial quality by evaluating 3 domains: selection, comparability, and outcome for cohort studies or exposure for case-control studies."
